prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D botanical illustration of a charming, slightly grumpy cartoon garden snail wearing a tiny, festive party hat, looking overwhelmed as it tries to carry a huge, beautifully detailed peony flower on its shell. Surrounding the snail is an elegant, nature-inspired arrangement of lush green ferns, delicate forget-me-nots, and whimsical fiddlehead ferns, all rendered in a soft, organic style. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the words "Happy Birthday, Johnny! Hope it's not too slow." The overall tone is humorous and lighthearted, set against a clean, off-white background.
